msgstr "Åbn menu"

#: pika-backup-common/src/borg/error.rs:31
msgid ""
"Retrieving encryption password from the keyring failed. Pika Backup requires "
"a keyring daemon (“secret service”) to store passwords. For installation "
"instructions see the operating system documentation."
msgstr ""
"Krypteringsadgangskoden kunne ikke hentes fra nøgleringen. Pika Backup "
"kræver en nøgleringsdæmon (“hemmelig tjeneste”) for at gemme adgangskoder. "
"Du kan finde installationsinstruktioner i dokumentationen til styresystemet."

#: pika-backup-common/src/borg/error.rs:33 pika-backup/src/utils.rs:279
msgid "The operation terminated unexpectedly."
msgstr "Handlingen afsluttede uventet."

#: pika-backup-common/src/borg/error.rs:34
msgid "This delete operation would delete too many archives."
msgstr "Denne slette-handling vil slette for mange arkiver."

#: pika-backup-common/src/borg/error.rs:35
msgid "No files selected to be included into backup."
msgstr "Ingen filer valgt til at blive inkluderet i sikkerhedskopien."

#: pika-backup-common/src/borg/error.rs:96
msgid "Timeout"
msgstr "Tidsgrænse"

#: pika-backup-common/src/borg/error.rs:143
msgid "Completed"
msgstr "Fuldført"

#: pika-backup-common/src/borg/error.rs:173
msgid "Aborted on user request."
msgstr "Afbrudt af brugeren."

#: pika-backup-common/src/borg/error.rs:175
msgid "Aborted because only metered connection was available."
msgstr "Afbrudt fordi kun en forbrugsbaseret forbindelse var tilgængelig."

#. Translators: Running backup was aborted because computer running on battery
#: pika-backup-common/src/borg/error.rs:179
msgid "Aborted because too long not connected to power."
msgstr "Afbrudt fordi strømforsyningen ikke har været tilsluttet i lang tid."

#: pika-backup-common/src/borg/error.rs:181
msgid "Aborted by system."
msgstr "Afbrudt af systemet."

#: pika-backup-common/src/borg/error.rs:182
msgid "The program or system seems to have crashed."
msgstr "Det lader til, at systemet eller programmet er gået ned."

#: pika-backup-common/src/borg/error.rs:183
msgid "{}"
msgstr "{}"

#: pika-backup-common/src/borg/error.rs:185
msgid "Unable to access backup repository: {}"
msgstr "Kunne ikke tilgå opbevaringssted til sikkerhedskopi: {}"

#: pika-backup-common/src/borg/error.rs:297
msgid ""
"A repository already exists at this location. Try the “Use Existing "
"Repository” option or select a different location."
msgstr ""
"Der findes allerede et opbevaringssted på denne placering. Prøv "
"indstillingen “Brug eksisterende opbevaringssted” eller vælg en anden "
"placering."

#: pika-backup-common/src/borg/error.rs:300
msgid ""
"Inconsistencies were detected in the repository. Running a data integrity "
"check is needed."
msgstr ""
"Der blev fundet uoverensstemmelser på opbevaringsstedet. Det er nødvendigt "
"at køre en dataintegritetskontrol."

#: pika-backup-common/src/borg/error.rs:302
msgid "No repository exists at this location."
msgstr "Der findes ikke et opbevaringssted på denne placering."

#: pika-backup-common/src/borg/error.rs:304
msgid "Not enough free space in repository."
msgstr "Ikke nok fri plads på opbevaringsstedet."

#: pika-backup-common/src/borg/error.rs:307
msgid "The configured location does not contain a valid repository."
msgstr ""
"Den konfigurerede placering indeholder ikke et gyldigt opbevaringssted."

#: pika-backup-common/src/borg/error.rs:310
msgid ""
"The configured location does not contain a valid repository configuration."
msgstr ""
"Den konfigurerede placering indeholder ikke en gyldig konfiguration for "
"opbevaringsstedet."

#: pika-backup-common/src/borg/error.rs:313
msgid "The configured location does not exist."
msgstr "Den konfigurerede placering findes ikke."

#: pika-backup-common/src/borg/error.rs:316
msgid "The selected location does already exist."
msgstr "Den valgte placering findes allerede."

#: pika-backup-common/src/borg/error.rs:319
msgid ""
"The repositories storage quota has been reached. Try deleting older archives "
"that are no longer needed."
msgstr ""
"Opbevaringsstedernes lagerkvote er nået. Prøv at slette ældre arkiver, der "
"ikke længere er brug for."

#: pika-backup-common/src/borg/error.rs:322
msgid ""
"Permission to access the configured location has been denied. Check the file "
"permissions."
msgstr ""
"Tilladelse til at få adgang til den konfigurerede placering er blevet "
"nægtet. Kontrollér filtilladelserne."

#: pika-backup-common/src/borg/error.rs:327
msgid ""
"A newer version of Pika Backup is required to access this repository. The "
"repository uses unsupported features."
msgstr ""
"Der kræves en nyere version af Pika Backup for at få adgang til dette "
"opbevaringssted. Opbevaringsstedet bruger funktioner, der ikke understøttes."

#: pika-backup-common/src/borg/error.rs:332
msgid "The selected location already contains a repository."
msgstr "Den valgte placering indeholder allerede et opbevaringssted."

#: pika-backup-common/src/borg/error.rs:335
msgid "The configured location does not contain an archive."
msgstr "Den konfigurerede placering indeholder ikke et arkiv."

#. RC 50+
#: pika-backup-common/src/borg/error.rs:339
msgid "Invalid encryption password."
msgstr "Ugyldig adgangskode til kryptering."

#. RC 60+
#: pika-backup-common/src/borg/error.rs:342
msgid "Repository access was aborted"
msgstr "Adgang til opbevaringssted blev afbrudt"

#. RC 70+
#: pika-backup-common/src/borg/error.rs:345
msgid "Failed to lock repository."
msgstr "Kunne ikke låse opbevaringssted."

#: pika-backup-common/src/borg/error.rs:346
msgid "Repository already in use."
msgstr "Opbevaringssted allerede i brug."

#: pika-backup-common/src/borg/error.rs:350
msgid "Connection closed by remote host."
msgstr "Forbindelsen blev lukket af fjernværten."

#: pika-backup-common/src/borg/error.rs:352
msgid "Connection to remote host broken."
msgstr "Forbindelsen til fjernværten er afbrudt."

#: pika-backup-common/src/borg/error.rs:356
msgid "Connection closed by remote host: “{}”"
msgstr "Forbindelsen blev lukket af fjernværten: “{}”"

#. General
#: pika-backup-common/src/borg/error.rs:360
msgid "Exception"
msgstr "Undtagelse"

#: pika-backup-common/src/borg/error.rs:362
msgid "Unspecified error."
msgstr "Uspecificeret fejl."

#: pika-backup-common/src/borg/functions.rs:279
msgid ""
"This backup repository is not encrypted at all, not even with a key stored "
"in plain text. Passwords can only be added to repositories that use "
"encryption."
msgstr ""
"Dette opbevaringssted til sikkerhedskopier er slet ikke krypteret, ikke "
"engang med en nøgle gemt i almindelig tekst. Adgangskoder kan kun tilføjes "
"til opbevaringssteder, der bruger kryptering."

